Task: Formula 1 Stats UI Draft
Project: Sport - Formula 1 Stats

Main Screens: #Home - #Races - #Drivers

Optional Screens: #Teams - #Circuits - #Event Results

--------------------------------------------------------

#Home 

[] Next Race
	[] Countdown Days, Hours, Minutes
	[] Circuit Name
	[] 1st, 2nd, 3rd Drivers Win Probability

[] Last Race
	[] DateTime
	[] Name - Country
	[] 1st, 2nd, 3rd Drivers
	[] Fastest Lap Driver

[] Team Ranks
	[] 1st Team - Points
	[] 2nd Team - Points
	[] 3rd Team - Points


--------------------------------------------------------

